_sText:
To use the map just unzip the files to your maps folder in your steam directory. It should contain gg_undertunnel.bsp and gg_undertunnel.nav. I give a special thanks to [-B-] for supplying the right science fiction textures and sky box.

This Map should be a fun and fast Gun Game map  with many levels, ladder, ramps, and environments. 

This is my first map so please comment and rate it so I know what to do and what not to do on the next map I create. 

Please Enjoy my map!!
